---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description={`Affiliate disclosure for ${SITE.name}.`}
>
  <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
  <p class="dek">Last updated: May 4, 2026</p>

  <p>
    Some links on {SITE.name} may be affiliate links. If you book a hotel, buy a
    book, reserve a tour, or purchase another product through those links, this
    publication may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.
  </p>

  <h2>How We Use Affiliate Links</h2>
  <p>
    Affiliate links should appear only when they are relevant to the article:
    for example, a historical site connected to the topic, nearby lodging for a
    history-focused trip, or a book that helps readers go deeper.
  </p>

  <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
  <p>
    Affiliate relationships do not decide what we write. Historical judgment,
    source quality, and reader usefulness come first.
  </p>

  <h2>Current Link Types</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Accommodation search links</li>
    <li>Book links</li>
    <li>Tour or activity links</li>
    <li>Map links to historical sites</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Questions</h2>
  <p>
    For questions about sponsorship or affiliate links, contact us through
    <a href={SITE.substackUrl}>Substack</a>.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
